    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable and stylish upgrade? This fantastic vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for your daily commute or weekend getaways! It runs smoothly and reflects the care it has received over the years. Don't miss out on this well-kept ride that's ready for many more miles of memories!",
