    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is fully functional for daily use. While the engine starts and runs reliably, it shows signs of age with some minor fluid seepage and a noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. The exterior has several scratches and minor dings consistent with its history, but there is no major structural damage. This is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections and minor upcoming maintenance needs.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation without the high price tag of a newer model. It starts, runs, and drives well, though it does show visible signs of wear including some minor scratches on the exterior and noticeable thinning of the upholstery inside. While it has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, a buyer should expect some typical age-related quirks and may want to address minor cosmetic repairs down the line. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes function over perfection.",
      "price": 18500.0,
