      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This motorcar exhibits an uncompromising standard of excellence, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments. Mechanically superior and rigorously inspected by our master technicians, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands peerless quality. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, ensuring an ownership experience that is as rewarding as it is exclusive.",
      "price": 48500.0,
